{"tid":511171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小朋友 X 大姐姐】為媾靚模 泰小學生贈 iPhone X","createTime":"2017-12-27T07:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T08:35:34.000Z","uid":3514,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a203b548044762ba16edf6babff2aba4e3b4dc40","tid":511171,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"現在的小學生簡直是要逆天了，別看他們年紀小，撩妹技能卻不輸老司機！據泰媒報導，曼穀的網紅小學生Nantapong Kidwanpattana近日在Facebook曬圖，一位女模靠在自己肩頭。兩人不僅共看電影，甚至還去手機賣場買了iPhone X手機。<br />\n<br />\n當然，Nantapong說這是他花47000泰銖(約合9385元人民幣)買的，作為聖誕禮物和愛的回報給妹子。<br />\n<br />\n由於約會照片很多舉止十分親密，網友也是紛紛調侃逗趣&ldquo;是不是作業太少？&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20171227/5/43/2/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E6%92%A9%E5%AB%A9%E6%A8%A1%E8%B2%B7iPhone-X%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%B0%91-8289157.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F5%2F43%2F2%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2592%25A9%25E5%25AB%25A9%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E8%25B2%25B7iPhone-X%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B0%2591-8289157.html&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6a6aa8e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20171227/5/43/2/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E6%92%A9%E5%AB%A9%E6%A8%A1%E8%B2%B7iPhone-X%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%B0%91-8289157.html</a><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘係大姐姐幹小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"